<HEADLINE> von Stade Sings at Graduation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	INCLINE VILLAGE, Nev. (AP) -- Tiny Sierra Nevada College received  
a graduation present from opera star Frederica von Stade at her 
stepdaughter's commencement. 
</P>
<P>
