<HEADLINE>  Indy 500 Crash Report </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	INDIANAPOLIS (AP) -- Crashes during practice for the May 30  
Indianapolis 500, with date, driver, car number, chassis-engine and 
description of the crash (r-rookie): 
</P>
