and stopped in the middle of the fourth turn. The car had extensive 
damage to the right side. Harrington was not injured. 
</P>
<P>
	4, May 17 -- Billy Boat, No. 11, Dallara-Aurora, went into the  
wall coming out of the third turn and came to rest in the north 
chute between turns three and four. The car had right-side damage. 
Boat was not injured. 
